{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"080ffa9fa7","title":"转发华东局关于镇反应注意之点的电报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5bc1d26fc3","index":0,"year":1951,"month":1,"day":24,"articleId":"080ffa9fa7"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"8cca15d5d1","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"080ffa9fa7","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"子恢，即邓子恢，当时任中共中央中南局第三书记。剑英，即叶剑英，当时任中共中央华南分局第一书记。小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央西南局第一书记。仲勋，即习仲勋，当时任中共中央西北局第一书记。一波，即海一波，当时任中共中央华北局第一书记。高岗，当时任中共中央东北局书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0961c40949","type":"title","text":"转发华东局关于镇反应注意之点的电报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"080ffa9fa7"},{"id":"8cca15d5d1","type":"paragraph","text":"子恢，剑英，小平，仲勋，一波，高岗\"同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"080ffa9fa7"},{"id":"bd78e57098","type":"paragraph","text":"华东局给福建省委电所说肃反应注意之点，我以为是对的。即为了打落故焰，伸张民气，对能首惯能恶霸及确有证据的重要特务和会门头子，应当放手杀几批。为了不致弄错，使自已陷于被动，对尚无证据的特务及会门头子，应当进行侦察，取得确证，而不要随便捕人系人。分清这两种情况的界限是必要的，请你们转知所属注意为盼。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"080ffa9fa7"},{"id":"dff4d12ecb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"080ffa9fa7"},{"id":"db174077a2","type":"paragraph","text":"一月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"080ffa9fa7"}],"page":{"id":"4e01cd4013","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"080ffa9fa7","start":69,"end":69}}}},"__N_SSG":true}